2000;;XChange;;Canadian;;Allan Moyle;;Stephen Baldwin, Kim Coates, Kyle MacLachlan, Pascale Bussi√®res, Janet Kidder;;science fiction;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/XChange_(film);;In the future, where it's faster to travel by exchanging bodies with someone at the destination, a man's body is hijacked by a ruthless terrorist.Toffler (Kim Coates), a member of the privileged "Corpie" (corporate) class, accidentally ends up in the body of a terrorist named Fisk (Kyle MacLachlan), who has in turn taken over Toffler's original body. Unable to continue as Fisk, Toffler is forced to use a cloned body (Stephen Baldwin) with a limited lifespan, in order to track down Fisk and get his original body back.